":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:49:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人地係你屋企食下烏蠅昆蟲 做咩要趕人走啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細到咁食到烏蠅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不用分得那麼細"},{"pid":"a779b1b3a0aaf34e15aa3944cc9c83b71ebbea2c","tid":390173,"uid":33789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人地係你屋企食下烏蠅昆蟲 做咩要趕人走啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細到咁食到烏蠅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似食蟻</blockquote><br />\n食曱甴蛋同bb,有佢就無其他害蟲,但預左間中要幫佢抹屎"},{"pid":"684716e55d2f035fa6ec09a9c71c1c9ba14f1ead","tid":390173,"uid":111476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解呢隻可以咁黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未見過咁黑色，見過通常都係偏灰白</blockquote><br />\n係囉 想問下樓主是咪捉左之後先變咁黑"},{"pid":"6f898d1df5e6fd6ec93d22ca345936a903974a94","tid":390173,"uid":111476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人地係你屋企食下烏蠅昆蟲 做咩要趕人走啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細到咁食到烏蠅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似食蟻</blockquote><br />\n食曱甴蛋同bb,有佢就無其他害蟲,但預左間中要幫佢抹屎</blockquote><br />\n我本身住村 記得有次我阿叔食飽飯無嘢做 知道D爬爬成日捐入牆上面兩盞燈入面 跟住屎忽痕搵螺絲批扭左個兩盞燈出來<br />\nD四腳爬爬蛋好似六合彩搞珠咁撚樣碌哂出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全部都得個殼 原來俾佢地攞左黎做育嬰室"},{"pid":"9ae2fa5f1ba43ea02163dcb9d2c9f456bf83092a","tid":390173,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:57:15.000Z","msg":"黑過黑鮑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4806fc0c87a5f514d309c057709ba84c58a029d8","tid":390173,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:13:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解呢隻可以咁黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未見過咁黑色，見過通常都係偏灰白</blockquote><br />\n係囉 想問下樓主是咪捉左之後先變咁黑</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/101046_e9f2fe19256d73fa2411923023860b79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F101046_e9f2fe19256d73fa2411923023860b79.jpg&h=d511db5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/101046_d00fae51d0ef3befefd0ef6c11d4d3d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F101046_d00fae51d0ef3befefd0ef6c11d4d3d1.jpg&h=9080adfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開閃光燈就咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/101239_3d61f4abad87e0a1ef07a7235b0f7e82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F101239_3d61f4abad87e0a1ef07a7235b0f7e82.jpg&h=aaf72990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔開就咁"},{"pid":"b0f0f4f3f399a2581fd8ad055d634c7c1b41df7b","tid":390173,"uid":111476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解呢隻可以咁黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未見過咁黑色，見過通常都係偏灰白</blockquote><br />\n係囉 想問下樓主是咪捉左之後先變咁黑</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/101046_e9f2fe19256d73fa2411923023860b79.jpg\" data